### C.2 Training-dynamics decomposition（6 ckpt × 20 traj）

**Q1 Cross-checkpoint Spearman（per-traj obs_nll, n=20）**

| | base | step50 | step75 | step100 | step125 | step150 |
|---|:-:|:-:|:-:|:-:|:-:|:-:|
| base | 1.000 | 0.926 | 0.905 | 0.854 | 0.867 | 0.899 |
| step50 | | 1.000 | 0.988 | 0.960 | 0.970 | 0.982 |
| step75 | | | 1.000 | 0.979 | 0.986 | 0.991 |
| step100 | | | | 1.000 | 0.988 | 0.969 |
| step125 | | | | | 1.000 | 0.983 |

base → step100 的 0.854 是最大的 rank 重排（§9.4）。

**Q2 Per-checkpoint succ/fail AUC（traj 级, n=10+10）**

| ckpt | succ mean | fail mean | gap | AUC | p |
|---|:-:|:-:|:-:|:-:|:-:|
| **base** | 1.947 | 2.174 | **−0.227** | **0.355** | 0.29 |
| step50 | 1.571 | 1.639 | −0.068 | 0.440 | 0.68 |
| step75 | 1.595 | 1.648 | −0.054 | 0.470 | 0.85 |
| step100 | 1.543 | 1.558 | −0.015 | 0.510 | 0.97 |
| step125 | 1.577 | 1.583 | −0.006 | 0.485 | 0.94 |
| step150 | 1.594 | 1.608 | −0.014 | 0.465 | 0.82 |

**Q3 Δ(step_k − base) —— 累积训练 drift（核心信号源）**

| Δ | mean | succ mean | fail mean | gap | AUC | p |
|---|:-:|:-:|:-:|:-:|:-:|:-:|
| step50 − base | −0.455 | −0.376 | −0.535 | +0.159 | **0.820** | **0.017** |
| step75 − base | −0.439 | −0.352 | −0.526 | +0.173 | 0.810 | 0.021 |
| step100 − base | −0.510 | −0.404 | −0.616 | +0.213 | 0.835 | 0.013 |
| step125 − base | −0.481 | −0.370 | −0.591 | +0.221 | 0.845 | 0.010 |
| step150 − base | −0.460 | −0.353 | −0.566 | +0.213 | **0.860** | **0.007** |

**Q3b Δ(step_k − step_{k-1}) —— 连续 ckpt drift（信号几乎消失）**

| Δ | gap | AUC | p |
|---|:-:|:-:|:-:|
| step50 − base | +0.159 | 0.820 | 0.017 |
| step75 − step50 | +0.014 | 0.640 | 0.31 |
| step100 − step75 | +0.039 | 0.705 | 0.13 |
| step125 − step100 | +0.009 | 0.620 | 0.38 |
| step150 − step125 | −0.008 | 0.455 | 0.76 |

→ **信号几乎全部集中在"base → step50"首段累积量**，其后连续 drift 无 outcome 信息（§9.5）。

**Q4 方差分解（total SS = 17.25）**

| 来源 | SS | % |
|---|:-:|:-:|
| between-traj | 12.85 | **74.5 %** |
| between-ckpt | 3.73 | 21.6 % |
| traj × ckpt | 0.67 | **3.9 %** |

**Q5 Rank stability 按 succ/fail 拆解**

| ckpt vs base | all | succ-only | fail-only |
|---|:-:|:-:|:-:|
| step50 | 0.926 | 0.900 | 0.827 |
| step75 | 0.905 | 0.879 | 0.806 |
| **step100** | 0.854 | **0.903** | **0.692** |
| **step125** | 0.867 | **0.903** | **0.680** |
| step150 | 0.899 | 0.900 | 0.768 |

Succ 轨迹排序恒定（≈0.90），fail 轨迹在 step 100–125 大幅重构（0.69）——§9.4 机制来源。

